          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">Vera Lynn and the ‘We’ll Meet Again’ Hypothesis <span class="texto2">by <a href="../../glasgowvoices/kate_mcloughlin/bio.php" class="link3">Kate McLoughlin</a></span></td>
